<BODY>
<H1><IMG ALIGN=LEFT
SRC="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/images/esdlogo-small.gif"> Oak Ridge
National Laboratory (ORNL)<br>
Environmental Sciences Division(ESD)<br>
Annual Information Meeting Agenda</H1>

<dl>
<dd>Wednesday, May 24, 1995
<dd>8:15 - 4:30 EDT
<dd>ORNL Building 1505, D. J. Nelson Auditorium
</dl>

<hr>
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT ALT="MBONE"
SRC="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/images/mbone.gif">
<IMG ALIGN=RIGHT ALT="DISH"
SRC="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/images/dish.gif">

For convenience, the presentations were broadcast over the <a
href="http://www-internal.ornl.gov/ORNL/broadband_locations.html">Oak
Ridge Interplant Broadband</a> and the <a
href="http://www.es.net/hypertext/services/group-page.html#mbone">ESnet
MBONE</a> (see <a
href="http://www.epm.ornl.gov/~dunigan/mbone.html">MBONE at ORNL</a>).
Other viewing areas in Building 1505 included Conference Room 190 and
the auditorium lobby.<P>

