<I>Raymond A. McCord</I><P>

Raymond McCord reviewed the types of spatial data available for all of
the Oak Ridge Reservation (ORR) and surrounding region and showed
examples of environmental and geographic data that have been generated
through remote sensing and mapping technology.  Data are available for
a variety of periods.  Significant improvements in spatial information
processing technology continue to expand the horizons of environmental
research.<P>

