<DOCOLDNO>IA001-000005-B039-202</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.esd.ornl.gov:80/info-meeting/southworth.html 128.219.24.7 19970101044122 text/html 3282
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
