<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Transport, Fate, and Effects of Contaminants in the
Clinch River and Watts Bar Reservoir</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1><IMG
SRC="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/images/esdlogo-small.gif"> Transport,
Fate, and Effects of Contaminants in the Clinch River and Watts Bar
Reservoir</H1>

<I>Robert B. Cook</I><P>

Five decades of operations and waste disposal activities at DOE
facilities located on the Oak Ridge Reservation in East Tennessee have
introduced a variety of contaminants into the Clinch River-Watts Bar
Reservoir system downstream from the reservation.  In compliance with
environmental regulations, the <A
HREF="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/programs/CRERP/">Clinch River Remedial
Investigation</A> of the off-site surface water contamination is a
component of the comprehensive DOE Environmental Restoration Program at
Oak Ridge.  The Clinch River Remedial Investigation was conducted
during the past 5 years to determine the nature, magnitude, and sources
of risks to humans and the environment in Poplar Creek, Clinch River,
and Watts Bar Reservoir.  This presentation summarized the distribution
of contaminants in fish, water, and sediments; discussed the transport
and fate of contaminants in the river-reservoir system; and showed the
initial results of the risk assessments.<P>

<HR>
<A HREF="cook.au"><IMG ALT="[Audio]" SRC="/images/sound.xbm"> Listen to Cook's talk</A>
<HR>

<H5><IMG SRC="cook.gif"><br>
Examples of scientific visualization of bathymetry and core data were
demonstrated by Cook.</H5>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
<I>ROBERT (Bob) B. COOK became head of the Environmental Chemistry
Section in ESD in 1995.  He also serves as manager of the <A
HREF="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/programs/CRERP/">Clinch River
Environmental Restoration Program</A>.  Bob earned a Ph.D. in
Geochemistry from Columbia University in 1981.  Since coming to ORNL in
1986, Bob has worked on projects dealing with aqueous and sediment
geochemistry; biogeochemistry; lake and stream acidification; and
contaminant transport, behavior, and fate.</I>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

<HR>
<ADDRESS><A HREF="index.html">ESD Annual Information Meeting, 1995</A>
/ <A HREF="/~forrest">webmaster@www.esd.ornl.gov</A>
