<IMG SRC="IMAGES/IMAGE25.JPG">
</CENTER><P>

<LI> When you return from the field check to see if anyone else is
using the base station.  If not turn off receiver to save the file.  If
someone else is using the base station do not turn off the receiver.
You can still download the active file following the suggestions in <A
HREF="HOSEGPS.HTM"><B>Downloading Data Files From
Receivers</B></A>.<P>

</OL>

