<H3><IMG SRC="photos/or.gif" ALT="Photograph of Scarburo Road Intersection">
</H3>

<H3>Land Use Planning </H3>

<P>
The City of Oak Ridge asked us to provide an aerial photograph
of the intersection of Scarboro and Union Valley roads outside
the Oak Ridge Y12 plant. Because of the number of traffic accidents
at this intersection the City of Oak Ridge plans to add a turn
lane. An aerial photograph makes the planning of this and similar
construction activities easier. 
<P>
