<TITLE>Short Rotation Forests Handbook</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY
BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#238E23" LINK="#855e42" VLINK="#5c3317" ALINK="#000000">
<H2>Short Rotation Forests Handbook</H2>
<P>The new edition of the <B><I>Handbook on How to Grow Short Rotation
Forests</I></B> will be available for distribution in May 1996. Much information
has been updated since the 1992 edition and chapters for two more countries,
Finland and the Netherlands, have been added. The price for a completely new
version with a binder is 250SEK (about $38US). A loose leaf version without
binder will cost 80 SEK (about $26US).</P>
<P>For additional information, contact</P>
<CENTER>
<P> <B>Marianne Mattsson<BR>SLU, Department of Short Rotation Forestry<BR>P.O.
Box 7016<BR>S-750 07 Uppsala<BR>Sweden<BR>Fax: +46 18 673440</B></P></CENTER>
<HR>
<P><A HREF="../index.html" TARGET="_top"><IMG
SRC="../images/bintiny.gif" ALT="Go to Biofuels Information Network" ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="25" HEIGHT="25"></A>
<BR><I><SMALL>File modified October 22, 1996</SMALL></I></P></BODY></HTML>
