<H2><FONT COLOR="#000080">Ordering information for Bioenergy '96 and ASAE
Liquid Fuel Conference Proceedings</FONT></H2>
<P>To order <B>Bioenergy '96 proceedings</B>, contact SERBEP, P.O. Box 1010,
CEB 3A, Muscle Shoals, AL 35662-1010. Proceedings are US $35 (US $40 outside the
United States) and checks should be made payable to TVA. Visa and Mastercard are
also accepted. Credit card orders may be faxed to SERBEP at +1 205 386 2963,
with pertinent card information and signature. 
</P>
<P>To order <B>ASAE Third Liquid Fuel proceedings</B>, contact the ASAE Order
Department at +1 616 428 6324, fax 616-429-3852. ASAE proceedings are $46 for
members and $56 for nonmembers plus $3.75 shipping and handling.</P></BODY></HTML>
