<P>In-field production costs for options 1 and 2 based on 50% moisture content
are shown in Table 5. They range from $3.09 to $11.94/dry Mg ($2.81 to
$10.83/dt). Silage transport costs add $8.37/dry Mg ($7.60/dt).</P>
<P></P>
