Regional-Scale GIS-Based Modeling System for Evaluating the Potential Cost and
Supplies of Biomass from Biomass Crops,&quot; working paper to be published in
<I>Bioenergy '96 Proceedings</I>. Nashville, Tennessee, 1996.
</LI>
<LI> U.S. Census Bureau. <I>Census of Agriculture 1992</I>, Alabama, Volume 1.
</LI></OL>
