Raise Switchgrass Yields Based on 10 Years of Research in Alabama.&quot; <I>Proc.
2nd Biomass Conf. of the Americas</I>, Portland, Oregon. Aug. 21-24, 1995.
</LI>
<LI> Cundiff, J.S. &quot;Simulation of Five Large Round Bale Harvesting Systems
for Biomass.&quot; In B.E. Dale (ed.) <I>Liquid Fuels, Lubricants and Additives
from Biomass</I>. <I>Proc. Alt. Energy Conf.</I>, Kansas City, Missouri. June
16-17, 1994.
</LI>
