sometimes frustrating path to this solution, and who obtained the DLG
river boundary file used in the final product.  Mike Weir, ESRI
instructor, made helpful initial suggestions about how to attack the
problem.  <A HREF="http://www.esd.ornl.gov/~forrest">Forrest
Hoffman</A> provided assistance with html markup of this document.</P>

