HREF="http://www.cecer.army.mil/grass/viz/sg3d.html">SG3D</A> with help
from <A HREF="http://www.cecer.army.mil/grass/viz/viz_group.html">Bill
Brown and Helena Mitasova</A>.  Special thanks to <A
