<ul>
<li> DNA-Tagged Microspheres'
<li> Fracture Interconnectivity
<li> Capture Zone
<li> Lead to monitoring well design
</ul>
</font>
<br clear="all">

<br>
<center><p><b>Figure 2:  Multiple tracers have been used at this site
to study fracture flow and transport under ambient and stressed
conditions.  Helium data demonstrate dominantly strike-preferential
flow under ambient conditions.  Colloid tracer studies using multilevel
wells are delineating fracture interconnectivity.</b></p></center>

